Module com.electra.canbusdemo
Package com.electra.canbusdemo

Class DeviceId

java.lang.Object
com.electra.canbusdemo.DeviceId
public final class DeviceId extends Object
Class containing static final String constants representing device IDs for CANbus communication.

The DeviceId class provides a set of public constants that represent unique identifiers for different devices in a CANbus network. These constants are used to distinguish between various messages and commands exchanged between components of the CANbus system.
